    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC introduces a new transport mechanism for TCP based upon partial ordering.  The aim is to present the concepts of partial ordering and promote discussions on its usefulness in network communications.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
